p: It can be seen that 88.59 % was oxygenated monoterpene, the high percentage of this class is due to the high percentage of trans-geraniol (lemonol) (35.38 %), α-citral (20.37 %), β-citral (14.76 %), cis-geraniol (7.38 %), DL-camphor (1.95 %), eucalyptol (1.63 %), thymol (1.28 %), β-linalool (1.17 %) and others comprising less than 1 % of the constituents.
